title: Aleksandrs Jeļisejevs
text:
Aleksandrs Jelisejevs (born 11 August 1971) is a retired <a href="Latvia">Latvia</a>n international <a href="association%20football">football</a> striker. He obtained a total number of 37 caps for the <a href="Latvia%20national%20football%20team">Latvia national football team</a>, scoring four goals. He also played in <a href="Finland">Finland</a>, <a href="Hungary">Hungary</a>, <a href="Russia">Russia</a> and <a href="Israel">Israel</a> during his career.
Honours.
National Team
Skonto FC
